      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为Education_LMS_Portal项目画一个Git流程图，重点展示main分支和develop分支之间的双向合并关系。标题就用\"Two-way merges (Education_LMS_Portal)\"吧。",
