      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把这部分画出来：main初始commit，branch develop，checkout develop做commit，然后checkout main merge develop。接下来呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "develop",
        "commit",
