      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下完整流程：main commit → develop分支commit → 合并到main → main再commit → 合并到develop → develop再commit → 最后合并回main。总共三次合并，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
